name: Pin Stripe No. 1 - LDS Baptism Invitation
description:
The significance of your child's baptism day is emphasized in this beautiful card. Printed on luxurious 130# acid free stock, this card will be a treasured keepsake of her special day. 

After purchase, please email info@primary-papers.com with the following information:
1) Child's FULL name to be printed on card
2) Baptism date
3) Baptism time
4) Address of baptism
5) Any other information you wish to have printed on card (luncheon, gathering information)
6) Photo(s) of your child. If you don't know which to choose, send several.

Digital proofs will be returned for your approval. Following your approval of the digital proof, your invitations will be printed and shipped within 5 business days. Rush orders are available.
